
This version of PerPlex is 6.8.9, the binary and data files of which are distributed here under the courtesy of James Connolly. They are compiled on a Linux system. 

The source codes of this version (along with other versions) can be found at https://perplex.ethz.ch/Perple_X_Sources_691/ as well as https://github.com/jadconnolly/Perple_X. 

If you would like to use this version on a different system (e.g., MAC or Windows) or adopt any recent versions, please follow the instruction of Perple_x, https://www.perplex.ethz.ch/ , to obtain the relevant files to compile them on your system. We unfortunately cannot offer direct help on compiling Perplex.  


